No. 79,

Orig.

Oklahoma v. Arkansas.

Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 *809days. Replies to such Exceptions, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
